title: The Football League Show 16.08.2014
description:
The Football League Show
Saturday 16th August 2014 

Highlights and analysis from the Football League. With the new season up and running there's an action-packed show as newly promoted Rotherham and Wolves go head-to-head at the New York Stadium. Plus extended highlights from Leeds v Middlesbrough and the best of the action as Bolton take on Nottingham Forest. IP RIP.
